	   <tr><td colspan=2>Doesn't work.&nbsp;&nbsp;One flaw that Verant issued to Barbarian Rogues is the fact that Slam or Bash, not sure of the name, and Backstab run on the same clock.  So if you DO succeed, the backstab won't land.  It's like when you get a successful Instill Doubt.  Try to backstab right after.  Won't work.  Why?  Same clock.  However if it last long, you can get a backstab in there.<br>&nbsp;<br>Formerly Ishkur D`Macbain<br>Now...Ishkur Leroux<br>Teir'Dal Dobluth<br><br>"So what if I stabbed him in the back.&nbsp;&nbsp;His back was to me!"</td></tr>
